<BaseLayout title="Troubleshooting">
  <p class="eyebrow">Docs</p>
  <h1>Troubleshooting</h1>
  <p>If install or runtime validation fails, inspect environment, backend support, and the resolved profile root first.</p>
  <pre><code>ankicli --json doctor env
ankicli --json doctor backend
ankicli --json doctor capabilities
ankicli --json profile resolve --name "User 1"</code></pre>
</BaseLayout>
